################################################################################
# Description: Explains what we want the code in the scoring directory to
# accomplish.
# Contributors: Connor Stone
# Date: 03-03-2016
################################################################################

# Objective
#-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Your function must take as an argument a list of players, a set of rules
for how each players score will be determined, and access to the database.
It must then assign a score to each player that is a prediction of the
score that they will achieve in the next game using the given rules.
